      "date": "2013-07-19 00:58:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/21ae1d88-f00b-11e2-b57b-52540035b04c).  Ran 15 tests.  No failures.",
