        "subject": "LU-3495 ptlrpc: Add history counter of handled requests",
        "message": "LU-3495 ptlrpc: Add history counter of handled requests\n\nThis patch helps to calculate the request handling rate\nof services between different time intervals. It collects\nenqueue RPC number every 10 seconds and keeps the PRC number\nduring last 100 seconds,1000 seconds and 10000 seconds by\ndefault. The time intervals can be set when inserting module.\nAnd the statistics can be accessed by /proc.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I7f09cbe3bc69b8b1fb7dfe54ea5b96a766e3fb17\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
